===Adjective===
'''hollow''' (''[[comparative]]'' '''hollower''' ''or'' '''more hollow''', ''[[superlative]]'' '''hollowest''' ''or'' '''most hollow''')

#Of something [[solid]], having an [[empty space]] inside.
#Of a sound, [[low-pitched]], and maybe [[scary]].
